2. 기본 속성

Tailwind 기본 속성
1) 레이아웃
display	        flex, grid, block, hidden
width / height	w-full, w-1/2, w-96, h-screen
spacing	        m-4, p-6, mt-2, px-3, space-y-2
position	    relative, absolute, top-0, left-1/2
z-index	        z-0, z-10, z-50

2) 텍스트
color	       text-gray-800, text-red-500
font-size	   text-sm, text-base, text-2xl
정렬	        text-left, text-center, text-right
font-weight	   font-normal, font-bold
줄간격	         leading-tight, leading-relaxed
자간	        tracking-wide, tracking-tighter

3) 배경
배경 색상 지정     bg-blue-100, bg-red-500
배경 이미지 설정    bg-cover, bg-center, bg-no-repeat
배경 그라데이션     bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-500

4) 테두리
border          border, border-0, border-2
border color    border-gray-300, border-red-500
테두리 radius     rounded, rounded-md, rounded-full
내부 요소 분할선    divide-x, divide-y, divide-gray-200

5) Flex & Grid 정렬
방향	    flex-row, flex-col
정렬	    justify-center, justify-between
정렬(세로)	 items-center, items-start
Grid	   grid, grid-cols-2, gap-4

6) 기타 유용한 속성들 
cursor        cursor-pointer, cursor-not-allowed
overflow      overflow-auto, overflow-hidden, scroll-smooth
opacity       opacity-50, opacity-100
transition    transition, duration-300, ease-in-out
visibility    invisible, visible
whitespace    whitespace-nowrap, break-words
hover         hover:bg-blue-600, hover:text-white
focus         focus:outline-none, focus:ring-2
shadow         shadow, shadow-lg, shadow-md